nodes.text: Deep Storage Bay V14 was a storage bay on Sel Zonn Station.

The storage bay was occupied by the droid Information broker Switch, who ran his organization from it. It was located on a level of the station with restricted access and Switch bribed the station's manager to keep it quarantined. A group of spacers once went there to negotiate with Switch for the release of some cargo and while they were there, they were attacked by Ganga Lor and his thugs.
